.RS
.RE
.TP
.B title.fontset
Default font for titles.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B title.page.barcode.symbology
When title.page.barcode.value is specified, this is the type of barcode
to generate.
Can either be one of the S1000D project configurable attribute values
